{"tid":2099864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"20.9萬人次在2月至5月免檢疫入境","createTime":"2020-07-08T14:39:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T14:39:45.000Z","uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"72a28e348d64557967095efdd54ea7fbb1c3a14e","tid":2099864,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:39:45.000Z","msg":"20.9萬人次在2月至5月免檢疫入境<br />\n<br />\n本港2月至5月一共有20.9萬人次獲免檢疫入境。<br />\n<br />\n 保安局書面回覆立法會質詢，透露向獲豁免人士發出醫學監察通知書的數字，指2月一共發出9.3萬張，3月發出3.9萬張，4月發出3.6萬張，5月發出4萬張。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346102\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2346102&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDK%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=92d27d87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2346102</a>"}]}